title: KTM 250 Duke vs Yamaha FZ-25 : Comparisons, News - India Today
text:
KTM 250 Duke vs Yamaha FZ-25 IndiaToday.in | New Delhi, February 23, 2017 | Written by Pratik Rakshit | UPDATED 18:08 IST 
Amid much speculation, KTM launched the all new 250 Duke in India, thus entering the 250cc segment. With this KTM will directly rival against the yet another new product, the Yamaha FZ-25, which was launched in January, 2017. 
Now that we have all the information about the new KTM 250 Duke, we compare the new bike with the Yamaha FZ-25 for a quick spec comparison.
